OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fwill move into the northeast tonight,
OL,7,Fextending slowly southwestwards across
OL,8,Feastern and central Scotland. Staying
OL,9,Fdry with clear spells elsewhere and a
OL,10,Fpatchy rural frost. Windy in the
OL,11,Fsouthwest, particularly around the
OL,12,Fcoast and Moors.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FCloud will linger along
OL,15,Fnortheast coasts on Wednesday. Plenty
OL,16,Fof sunshine for many and feeling warm.
OL,17,FHazy sunshine in the southwest with
OL,18,Fstrong winds and perhaps the odd
OL,19,Fafternoon shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
